relationships.description: A workspace group can be deleted by using the delete method.
The delete method can be called on a Workspace Group instance.
A workspace group can be forcibly deleted by setting the force argument to true.
Connecting to a free tier workspace requires downloading and setting an SSL certificate.
The includeTerminated parameter is used to include terminated workspaces in a workspace group query.
The select parameter is used to select specific fields from a workspace group.
Available size values for creating a workspace are referenced by the SingleStore Helios Pricing page.
The use method can optionally use a DatabaseSchema to describe the database schema.
The create method can optionally use a DatabaseSchema to describe the database schema.
The query method returns a query result as an array of RowType.
